---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 513
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Knowledge Through Faith
  - 170
By: Ahmed Et-Tahâwî
---
He who desires to know what is closed to him and whose reason is not
satisfied with resignation, is separated by his very desire from Union
with God, from pure knowing and from true faith; he wavers between
infidelity and faith.
